---
// src/pages/cafe/pastries-baked-goods.astro
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Fresh Pastries & Baked Goods | The Local Place Cafe"
  description="House-made pastries, croissants, muffins, scones, and baked goods in Centerville. Fresh daily, made from scratch. Order online or visit 111 S Public Square."
  keywords="pastries Centerville, fresh baked goods, croissants, muffins, scones, bakery Centerville TN"
>
  <!-- Schema markup placeholder for LocalBusiness + Menu -->
  <!-- TODO: Add JSON-LD schema for bakery items -->

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Fresh Pastries & Baked Goods</h1>
      <p>House-Made Daily. Flaky, Buttery, Worth the Calories</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cafe">Cafe</a></li>
        <li><span>Pastries & Baked Goods</span></li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Pastries Made Right Here</h2>
      <p>
        We don't truck these in frozen. We make them here. You can smell them baking from the street on a good morning. Croissants that flake when you bite them. Muffins that taste like someone's grandma made them—if that grandma actually knew what she was doing.
      </p>

      <h3>What We Bake</h3>
      <div class="menu-items">
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Croissants</h4>
          <p>Buttery, flaky layers that crumble just right. Plain or filled with chocolate. Fresh every morning.</p>
          <span class="price">$3-4</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Blueberry Muffins</h4>
          <p>Loaded with real blueberries, not stingy fake ones. Moist, fluffy, with a sugary top that crunches.</p>
          <span class="price">$3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Scones</h4>
          <p>Cranberry, lemon poppyseed, or cinnamon. Crumbly but not dry. Pair with coffee and you're set.</p>
          <span class="price">$3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Cinnamon Rolls</h4>
          <p>Warm, gooey, topped with cream cheese icing. Big enough to share. You won't want to.</p>
          <span class="price">$4</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Cookies</h4>
          <p>Chocolate chip, oatmeal raisin, snickerdoodle. Chewy centers, crispy edges. Fresh-baked daily.</p>
          <span class="price">$2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Danish Pastries</h4>
          <p>Fruit-filled or cheese. Flaky pastry, sweet filling, perfect with your morning espresso.</p>
          <span class="price">$3-4</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Banana Bread</h4>
          <p>Moist, rich, loaded with banana flavor. Not too sweet. Slice it thick.</p>
          <span class="price">$3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
          <h4>Brownies</h4>
          <p>Fudgy, dense, chocolatey. These aren't cake-like. They're the real deal.</p>
          <span class="price">$3</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Why Our Baked Goods Are Different</h3>
      <p>
        Here's what you won't find: preservatives, shortcuts, frozen dough from a truck. What you will find: real butter, fresh ingredients, recipes that actually work. We bake in small batches so you get them fresh, not leftovers from yesterday.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>House-made:</strong> We mix, roll, and bake everything here. No frozen shortcuts.</li>
        <li><strong>Fresh daily:</strong> Baked every morning. When we sell out, we're done for the day.</li>
        <li><strong>Real ingredients:</strong> Butter, not margarine. Real vanilla. Fresh fruit.</li>
        <li><strong>Small batches:</strong> Quality over quantity. Always.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Pair with Coffee</h3>
      <p>
        A croissant and a latte is a breakfast ritual for a reason. A scone and an americano? Chef's kiss. Order both online and pick them up together—nothing's better than biting into a warm pastry with hot coffee in your other hand.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Order Ahead</h3>
        <p>Want your pastry and coffee ready when you arrive? Order online and skip the line.</p>
        <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" class="cta-button">Order on Clover</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>What Customers Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-cards">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"I grabbed a croissant on a whim and it changed my whole morning. Flaky, buttery, still warm. Now I stop by every Friday before work."</p>
          <p><strong>- David (Local)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"The blueberry muffins are insane. My kids ask for them by name now. We've tried other bakeries—this one's better."</p>
          <p><strong>- Ashley & Family</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"Cinnamon rolls here are dangerous. Warm, gooey, covered in icing. I've stopped pretending I'll share them."</p>
          <p><strong>- Rachel (Regular)</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="location-info">
      <h2>Visit The Local Place Cafe</h2>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Hours</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Monday-Friday:</strong> 6 AM - 6 PM<br />
            <strong>Saturday:</strong> 9 AM - 6 PM<br />
            <strong>Sunday:</strong> Closed
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>
            111 South Public Square<br />
            Centerville, TN 37033<br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:(931)729-3481">(931) 729-3481</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Order Online</h3>
          <p>
            <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Order on Clover →</a><br />
            Skip the line. Pick up fresh.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #f4d4a8 0%, #d9a574 100%);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .menu-items {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .menu-item {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .menu-item h4 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .menu-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .price {
    display: block;
    color: #8b4513;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-box h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #8b4513;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #6b3410;
  }

  .testimonial-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .testimonial-card p:first-child {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .testimonial-card p:last-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .location-info {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .info-block {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .info-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .info-block p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .info-block a {
    color: var(--brown);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .info-block a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .menu-items {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
